dc_description_s: Relief show by 5 metres contour intervals (contours are approximate) and spot heights. Surveyed 1967-68. "Reg. no. 7749 HD'80 (D.O.9-1:13,333)-10706 '84." "Refer to this map as: 1:20,000 Chandigarh guide map, first edition." Relief show by 5 metres contour intervals (contours are approximate) and spot heights. Insets: Layout of Chandigarh (1:100,000); Routes to important places of tourist interest (1:1,000,000). "Surveyed 1967-68." Verso: "Bus routes", (1:30,000). Survey of India.
